{"tid":912194,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"資本充足性管理（Capital Adequacy Management）－你不可不知的銀行營運常識","createTime":"2018-11-22T12:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T11:11:02.000Z","uid":112161,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18da60858dc6d8c8c4b26f8e199ab5027c8664d3","tid":912194,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"銀行管理（三）／落雨人／2018年11月22日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/567419136975056/posts/774095706307397/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F567419136975056%2Fposts%2F774095706307397%2F&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgycn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=74e0d34c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/567419136975056/posts/774095706307397/</a><br />\n<br />\n銀行的營運主要牽涉到三方面的管理：流動資金管理（Liquidity Management）、資產負債管理（Asset and Liability Management）及資本充足性管理（Capital Adequacy Management）。這三方面的管理對於銀行的健康運作可以算得上是非常關鍵。上兩篇討論了流動資金管理及資產負債管理的重要性，筆者今次將會粗略講解銀行管理的另一方面－資本充足性管理。<br />\n<br />\n充足的資本有助確保銀行不會因為資產的損失而無法償還債務。這可透過以下例子來說明。假設有兩間銀行，其資產負債表如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJwuyfW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJwuyfW.png&h=183d89d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3x18Nw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3x18Nw.png&h=b058ac48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若市場表現不似預期，證券價格下跌10％，銀行的資產負債表中的證劵的價值亦隨之而下跌10％，或＄200。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJi8ONz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJi8ONz.png&h=b8cd7af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5CNmpkV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5CNmpkV.png&h=fe35b40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩間銀行同樣承受了＄200的證劵投資損失，銀行A仍可健康地生存下去，但銀行B的銀行資本卻變成了負數，面臨破產。由此可見，銀行資本越高，銀行的生存能力亦會越高。不過，銀行資本越高，其盈利表現卻會較遜色。<br />\n<br />\n上亦例子的兩間銀行的資產是完全相同的，若兩間銀行的資產回報均為＄500：<br />\n銀行A的股本回報率（Return on Equity）＝＄500／＄1,000＝50％；<br />\n銀行B的股本回報率（Return on Equity）＝＄500／＄100＝500％；<br />\n銀行B的盈利表現明顯優勝於銀行A。<br />\n<br />\n文章長度有限，深一步的探討，抑或其他話題，留待下篇再討論。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n參考資料及延伸閱讀<br />\n（1）Arnold G. 2012. Modern Financial Markets and Institutions: A Practical Perspective. Person Education.<br />\n（2）Casu, B. et al. 2006. Introduction to Banking. London: FT Prentice Hall.<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n無論正評負評，睇到咁後，多謝支持／批評！<br />\nFACEBOOK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rainingmanhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frainingmanhk%2F&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgycn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=49646be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rainingmanhk/</a><br />\n所有文章<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">近期正嘗試增加網站人流，得閒不妨點擊吓條link！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://rainingmanhk.wordpress.com/content/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frainingmanhk.wordpress.com%2Fcontent%2F&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgycn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7783da1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rainingmanhk.wordpress.com/content/</a>"},{"pid":"a77717c0f0e8a715d03de66a4687f2b4f2514098","tid":912194,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"👍🏻"},{"pid":"a84b95cb850908f42c42cf92d5f9b01d6dacbc94","tid":912194,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77717c0f0e8a715d03de66a4687f2b4f2514098","tid":912194,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"👍🏻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e8266b321996f9daf15c7dff93e1b901302764","tid":912194,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T14:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a0f96dcc24c0c35cc6f55d5c99c9198e6ff4d8",